### [2 Chronicles Chapter 27](../../../bib/kjv/ch2027.htm#001.md)

[2 Chronicles](../../../bib/kjv/ch2001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">ch2 27:0</span></span>

Overview

[Ch2 27:1](../../../bib/kjv/ch2027.htm#001.md), Jotham reigning well,
prospers; [Ch2 27:5](../../../bib/kjv/ch2027.htm#005.md), He subdues the
Ammonites; [Ch2 27:7](../../../bib/kjv/ch2027.htm#007.md), His reign and
death; Ahaz succeeds him.

